      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 50 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 50 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：鼎顛趾，利出否，得妾以其子，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows the caldron overthrown and its feet turned up. (But) there will be advantage in its getting rid of what was bad in it. (Or it shows us) the concubine (whose position is improved) by means of her son. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-050-ding__alignment-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">yijing</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">yijing-050-ding</prop>
