      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 50 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：鼎黃耳金鉉，利貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth six, divided, shows the caldron with yellow ears and rings of metal in them. There will be advantage through being firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
