      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 50 上九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 50 上九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：鼎玉鉉，大吉，无不利。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth NINE, undivided, shows the caldron with rings of jade. There will be great good fortune, and all action taken will be in every way advantageous.</seg>
      </tuv>
